Create PACKAGE.JSON file:
> npm init -y

Install webpack and webpack-cli as a dev dependencies
> npm install --save-dev webpack webpack-cli

Run script build from PACKAGE.JSON
> npm run build



Install Babel and stuff
> npm install babel-core babel-loader webpack-dev-server label-preset-env babel-polyfill --save-dev
  - babel-core         : main babel core
  - babel-loader       : 
  - webpack-dev-server : automatic live code updates
  - label-preset-env   : convert to
  - babel-polyfill     : expect native es6





